channel.title: "Hi"? Has this happened to anyone else?
channel.description:
So there i am, on rsbots.net, i bought an autominer pro auth, so i go to yahoo mail and open my inbox, and i get this "Message from webpage hi"
So i close it, thinking "wtf?"
Then not even a second later, it comes up again, this time i had the option to click "Dont show any more popup dialogs from this page" or whatever, so i checked that and it didnt come up.. I searched it on google, lots of other people were having this problem.. no one has the answer.. Could my browser be infected?
